title: Veegil

creator: Veegil
descriptionHtml:
The Veegil platform is a platform for civic engagement. A platform connecting the leaders, citizens and stakeholders in the polity where debates, discourse and myriad other interactions take place. Where all voices are heard.

* With this app, you are able to meet other citizens online and discuss issues you like.

* Explore users' profiles to learn about social and political experiences, issues or causes they care about, political campaigns they support and organizations that they are a members of or associated with.

* Follow and Connect with politicians across political parties and at different levels of government. Here you would find politicians and leaders at the local, state and federal government.

* Explore issues in the following categories: Politics, Election monitoring, Business, Economy, Culture, News, Legal (Law), Sports, Security, Health, Education, Technology, Agriculture, Transportation, Communication, Nature, General, Word of the Day, Today in History, Did you know and Others.

* Fact-check information with Veralog, our unique feature for addressing misinformation and questioning facts. Veralog uses artificial intelligence (A.I.) to help you determine the fact index of an information. The fact index communicates how much confidence you should have in the veracity of facts or statements on the platform. You can also veralog information you have encountered from outside the platform.

* Meet other Veegilants from Lagos, Abuja, Port Harcourt, Kano, Kaduna, and other cities and states across Nigeria.

* Get notifications on happenings in the platform.

* Follow and un-follow users

* Report abusive or inappropriate content or users

* Block abusive or inappropriate content or users

Made with love in Ota, Nigeria for Nigerians and the world!
